info.name: osu!purple (read description  for instruction)
info.description:
To make the style work follows the step below (I don't really getting as why my code has some error whenever I try to publish it while it work perfectly fine when I edited it -_-) :
1. open the link:
   https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Clg8ZByiLR8s2KV5FiFBPRpcDEBjeAqU/view?usp=sharing
2. download the .txt and copy the text
3. open your web > your stylish extension
4. go to editor and paste your code and click preview to make sure it's working perfectly.
5. if it's working perfectly fine then you're good to go and save the style
